-Iron-Maiden.-CREDIT_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden.-CREDIT_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden.-CREDIT_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden.-CREDIT_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden.-CREDIT_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden.-CREDIT_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden.-CREDIT_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Iron-Maiden">铁娘子的</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-dickinson">布鲁斯·狄金森（Bruce Dickinson）</a>宣布了一部新的图形小说，上面印有威廉·布雷克（William Blake）坟墓的土壤。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1023" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/iron-maiden-senjutsu-review-3035836"><b>铁娘子 - “ Senjutsu”评论：富有想象力的即时经典</b></a></li></ul><p>与Z2漫画一起，这位歌手现在揭开了<em>Mandrake Project：One Years</em> ，这是一部图形小说，该小说编译了他的<em>Mandrake Project Project</em>漫画系列的前四期，该系列于去年首次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maidens-bruce-dickin