oads/2025/03/coldplay-stromae-pomme@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coldplay-stromae-pomme@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coldplay-stromae-pomme@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coldplay-stromae-pomme@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/arcane"><em>Arcane</em></a>宣布了以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>为特色的热门歌曲“ Ma Meil​​leure Ennemie”的扩展版 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/arcane-netflix-season-2-underrated-shows-3769686">为什么“奥术”是Netflix最被低估的系列</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚，Instagram上的官方<em>Arcane</em>帐户宣布了扩展版本，该版本将于下周发布（4月4日）。这首歌将使Coldplay与曲目的原始歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stromae">Stromae</a>和Pomme合作<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/arcane-stromae-pomme-season-two-soundtrack-video-3847878">，不到一个月的时间发布了病毒在病毒击中的新视频后一个月</a>。</p><p> “ Ma Meil​​leure Ennemie”是由Stromae and Pomme在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/riot-games">Riot Games</a>的第二季和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a>的热门动画系列<em>Arcane</em>撰写和表演的，该系列Arcane基于流行的视频游戏<em>《英雄游戏联盟》</em> 。</p><p>您可以在<a href="https://arcane.lnk.to/mme-coldplay?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAabiq2risquEeE_S3h6l_8xJTDjpZbJxjmRnad-hG7aWYrefoHy0NcCZChU_aem_1G53wAHSvEAptkOys1Kwjw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处的</a>数字流媒体平台上预留以Coldplay为特色的“ Ma Meil​​leure Ennemie”的扩展切割。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHtW-QupuwU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px)