loads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Timothy-Norris_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Timothy-Norris_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Timothy-Norris_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Timothy-Norris_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Timothy-Norris_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Timothy-Norris_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Timothy-Norris_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran）</a>透露了他未来专辑的头衔，并说他受到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quentin-tarantino">昆汀·塔伦蒂诺（Quentin Tarantino）</a>的启发，将他的发行版限制为10。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ed-sheeran-autumn-variations-review-lyrics-tracklist-3505933">埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran） - “秋季变化”评论：南瓜辣酱</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（3月27日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-tonight-show-starring-jimmy-fallon"><em>由吉米·法伦（Jimmy Fallon）主演的《今晚秀》（Tonight Show</em></a> ）出现了“你的形状”歌手，在那里他分享了他即将发行的专辑的标题将是“ Play”。</p><p>这个消息是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-seemingly-reveals-title-of-new-album-3837991">在经过数周的戏弄之后</a>发布的，尽管LP尚未收到发布日期，但Sheeran继续透露，他的下一张专辑的头衔将受到唱片控件的影响。</p><p>他以前的专辑收藏的灵感来自数学符号（“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-ed-sheeran-12309-309122">plus</a> ”，“多重”，“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/ed-sheeran-divide-album-review-2000538">Divide</a> ”，“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ed-sheeran-review-subtract-lyrics-3439379">Subtract</a> ”和“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ed-sheeran-review-3081750">equals</a> ”），他告诉Fallon，下一个系列将包括“暂停”，“快速前进”，“ Rewind”和“ Stop&#39;之类的标题 - 他说他18岁时就说了他。</p><p> Sheeran还补充说，一旦该系列完成，他计划停止制作专辑。他说：“我想做10。我有点痴迷于[Quentin] Tarantino，我听说他正在拍10部电影，而且他有像<em>Grindhouse</em>这样的附带项目。” “我想做我的10，然后不时地做一个附带项目。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/awbaFPhoACA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他还建议他已经计划在遗传上发行，该发行将包含在他一生的几十年中写的歌曲，并将在他的死后发行。他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-is-already-planning-for-a-posthumous-album-3418059">首先在2023年暗示了这一点，并说这是“连续的工作”</a> 。</p><p>他告诉法伦说：“我有点想在我的一生中制作一张专辑，在那里您在其中写了不同的歌曲，然后在您的遗嘱中，它会在您死亡的那一天出来，而被称为“弹出”。”</p><p> “Imagine if when <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">[Paul] McCartney</a> passes away and there&#39;s a record that he&#39;s made that has a song from he&#39;s 16, there&#39;s a song from when he&#39;s 20, there&#39;s a song from when he&#39;s 30. It&#39;d be fascinating.” </p><figure id="attachment_3849998" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3849998" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3849998" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_FilmMagic.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ed-Sheeran.-CREDIT_-Dana-Jacobs_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3849998" class="wp-caption-text"> Ed Sheeran. CREDIT: Dana Jacobs/FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p> During his appearance, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-ed-sheeran-debut-nostalgic-new-song-old-phone-on-fallon-3849953">Sheeran also partially premiered a new song</a> , titled &#39;Old Phone&#39;, on acoustic guitar.他在赛道上发表讲话时透露，这首歌的灵感来自于他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nme-128-1202226">2016年对版权侵犯的主张的诉讼</a>。</p><p>本月初，希兰（Sheeran）确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-confirms-that-his-new-album-is-done-and-teases-single-3847662">“播放”的工作是“完成的”，正式单曲将“很快”到达</a>。该更新是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-ed-sheeran-debut-new-song-during-surprise-new-orleans-street-performance-3846796">在新奥尔良街头的惊喜设置之后，在那里他加入了一支铜管乐队，并最初首次亮相了新歌</a>。</p><p>同时，这位歌手此前曾透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-confirms-new-single-is-coming-next-month-reveals-upcoming-song-titles-3845335">一首名为“蓝宝石”的新歌将在未来几个月内发行</a>。他去社交媒体<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/EdSheeran/comments/1j4gn8m/azizam_321/?share_id=IV1m1Y5KzxmQKscGWgp7K&amp;utm_content=1&amp;utm_medium=ios_app&amp;utm_name=ioscss&amp;utm_source=share&amp;utm_term=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">回应了一个粉丝</a>，他问他应该在婚礼上演奏的他的哪首歌，说：“依靠你结婚时，很快就会有一些新的新选择。”</p><p>关于新音乐的暗示是因为Sheeran结束了2024年，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-reveals-hes-already-finished-his-new-album-3821440">透露他已经完成了下一个唱片</a>。他解释说：“感觉就像我很长一段时间以来第一次重返大流行音乐。”</p><p>这是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-is-working-on-new-music-but-it-wont-come-out-this-year-3753495">希拉（Sheeran）去年五月说他制作了一些新材料的情况</a>之后，但是等待了更长的时间来分享它。他告诉粉丝：“我去年在Tour上发行了两张唱片，在巡回演出和发行唱片上很多。</p><p>即将发行的专辑将标志着他自2023年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ed-sheeran-autumn-variations-review-lyrics-tracklist-3505933">“秋季变化”</a>以来的第一张专辑，标志着热门发行的后续作品<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ed-sheeran-review-subtract-lyrics-3439379">“  - （“减””）</a> 。据说后者是Sheeran长期以来的数学主题系列的最终作品。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-reveals-titles-of-his-next-five-albums-says-hell-stop-at-10-after-being-inspired-by-quentin-tarantino-3849995">Ed Sheeran reveals titles of his next five albums, says he&#39;ll stop at 10 after being inspired by Quentin Tarantino</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
